Release Notes
=============

November 29, 2017 Kevin Meagher (kmeagher@ulb.ac.be)
------------------------------------------------------------------
Release V00-04-02

* remove I3XMLSummaryServiceFactory from example
* doc cleanup
* script cleanup: remove `Finish()` and TrashCan

March 24, 2017 Kevin Meagher (kmeagher@ulb.ac.be)
------------------------------------------------------------------
Release V00-04-01

* Remove explicit scipy dependency
* Add serialization dependency
* Move examples to use gullivers shiny new OutputName parameter

May 2, 2016 Kevin Meagher (kmeagher@ulb.ac.be)
------------------------------------------------------------------
Release V00-04-00

* Added a replacement module for I3ParticleForgeModule.  We'll need this for Cascade L3 at the very least. (r137596)
* Add scipy dependency
* Switch to Sphinx docs
* add examples and unit tests
* add `std::` to `isnan()`
* remove `TweakAMANDAPulses`
* remove `IC40Correction`
* remove cruft and TODOs

