August 20, 2013 Meike de With (meike.de.with@desy.de)
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Release V00-03-02

- Add #ifndef NDEBUG and #endif around some log_trace messages to 
  avoid compiling problems in Release build
- Replace obsolete code (FillPhotonicsSource and CalcDistance) with
  newer code

  -- David Boersma

- Remove log4cplus dependency
- Make project compatible with Python 3
- Updates to be compatible with dataclasses trunk (no functional or
  non-backwards-compatible changes)

  -- Nathan Whitehorn

- Import dataio

  -- Jakob van Santen


