January 18, 2013 Emanuel Jacobi  (emanuel.jacobi@desy.de)
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Release V00-03-00

Feature:

- Added the parameter LightScale to let the user apply a constant
  correction factor to the photonics charge prediction.
  The default value is 1, so the user has to adjust it

  -- Eike Middell

- Make IC40 specific scaling of photonics amplitudes optional

  -- Hans Niederhausen

Bugfix:

- Clean up CLang warnings

  -- Kevin Meagher

- Remove dependency on FeatureExtractor in the test script

  -- Emanuel Jacobi


