December 04, 2009, Eike Middell
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Release V00-01-00

Initial release, code reviewed by Tom Feusels

Most changes since the last non-release trunk version are internally and don't
change the behaviour. The unused parameter "EventHypothesis" was removed.
Several unit tests and example scripts were added.


